				<div class="bookname">
					<h1>第六十六章:恶劣的题</h1>
					<div class="bottem1">
						<a id="pager_prev" href="3355632.html" target="_top" class="pre">上一章</a> ← <a id="pager_current" href="./" target="_top" title="" class="back">章节列表</a> → <a id="pager_next" href="3355634.html" target="_top" class="next">下一章</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="javascript:;" onclick="addBookMark(3355633,61583,'第六十六章:恶劣的题');">加入书签</a>
